The Sticks has several meanings:

''The Sticks'' is a term, usually pejorative, that refers to a remote, rural area; a place that is removed from civilization such as a [[Boondock]].

'''The Sticks''' is an Australian rock and roll band. Members include '''Paul Luciak''' (guitar), '''Bernard Chaplinski''' (guitar, lead vocals), '''Nick Brown''' (Drums) and '''Mikey Rumor''' (Bass) [http://www.thesticks.com.au]